No. 11-5101. William Keisling, Petitioner v. Richard K. Renn, et al. 565 U.S. 934, 132 S. Ct. 383,

181 L. Ed. 2d 241,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 6444, October 3, 2011.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

The Chief Justice took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.

Same case below, 425 Fed. Appx. 106.
